SUMMARY:Merge + Meet: Kickoff Meeting for Underrepresented Groups and Allies
DESCRIPTION:Don’t wait until the last day to find your people. Join the Merge Forward&nbsp\;team—whether you’re in one of our seven community groups (Women in Cloud Native\, Neurodiversity\, Friends of Dorothy\, and more) or an ally.&nbsp\;Meet peers \, swap contact info\, and head to your favorite sessions with your new crew.\n \nIn a world that runs remote and distributed\, the connections that stick are the ones you make in person. This kickoff is the place to introduce yourself\, connect with peers\, and build a small circle so your conference experience is stronger\, more supportive\, and more impactful from day one. \n\nLearn more about Merge Forward at https://community.cncf.io/merge-forward
CATEGORIES:INCLUSION + ACCESSIBILITY
LOCATION:G104 - 105 | Community Hub\, Amsterdam\, Netherlands
SEQUENCE:0
